      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>As a full action, a phentomite can alter her vision to detect the latent heat trails left by passing creatures. This allows the phentomite to use the @Compendium[sfrpg.skills.CzEAY60hUMyfOC4G]{Perception} skill to perform the follow tracks task of the @Compendium[sfrpg.skills.mcAqh41q55fTj1vl]{Survival} skill and also functions as the @Compendium[sfrpg.universal-creature-rules.nTS5FBfDAorzVb7n]{Tracking} universal creature rule. While this ability is active, the phentomite takes a &ndash;1 penalty to Reflex saving throws. The phentomite can deactivate this ability as a move action.</p>"
